name: leaflettitle
label: Leaflet title
description: A title or name given to the leaflet that belongs to this consent form. (DC:title )

name: leafletdate
label: Leaflet date
description: A point or period of time associated with the publication of this leaflet that belongs to this consent form. (DC:date )

name: leafletversion
label: Leaflet version
description: The version, edition, or adaptation of this leaflet that belongs to this consent form. (DC:hasVersion )

name: consentformidentifier
label: Consent form identifier
description: A unique proper name or character sequence that identifies this particular leaflet and consent form combination used in signing individual consent. Using a DOI would be optimal. Using any resolvable URL is suboptimal but still preferable over using a plain text value. (DC:identifier )

name: consentformtitle
label: Consent form title
description: A title or name given to this consent form. (DC:title )

name: consentformaccepteddate
label: Consent form accepted date
description: Date of acceptance of this consent form. (DC:dateAccepted )

name: consentformvaliduntil
label: Consent form valid until
description: End date of the validity of this consent form. (DC:valid )

name: consentformcreator
label: Consent form creator
description: Indicates the authoritative body who brought this consent form into existence. (DC:creator )

name: consentformversion
label: Consent form version
description: The version, edition, or adaptation of this consent form. (DC:hasVersion )
